  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b819085f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FlRIrvTGkm9vcu4PaD56cB6UCl6n8xWaOe8TAK91ohcTh6AnbrJibvXtSJbDGFEwqmhaPZKxeiaMQMzAqxSVFjXxohD0JMKN5BnsRicR3ulibkvM%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>在一些前沿模型突然变得不可用的时刻，我们选择相信另一条路：前沿智能不应只属于少数人，也不应被少数规则随时收回。它应该<span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">开放、可用、可构建，并服务于每一位开发者</span>。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>GLM-5.2 是智谱迄今能力最强的开源模型，支持真正可用的<span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;1M 上下文</span>，并在<span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">长程任务</span>中继续保持领先。它也依旧是我们心中最</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span>强的国产 Coding 模</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span>型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span>今晚 5:21，<span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">GLM-5.2 将面向 GLM Coding Plan 全量用户开放，覆盖 Lite / Pro / Max / 团队版。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span>GLM-5.2 API 将于下周上线，模型下周正式<span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">开源</span></span><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">，</span></span><span><span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">遵循 MIT 协议</span>。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>A step closer to frontier intelligence for everyone.</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>The future of AI is open, and it is for the people.</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 8px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\"><span><span>ModelKey：<span style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">GLM-5.2</span></span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱宣布 GLM-5.2 模型全量开放，支持 1M 上下文，下周开源并遵循 MIT 协议，强调前沿智能的开放与可用性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱宣布 GLM-5.2 模型全量开放，支持 1M 上下文，下周开源并遵循 MIT 协议，强调前沿智能的开放与可用性。",
  "summary": "智谱于 2026 年 6 月 13 日发布公告，宣布其最新模型 GLM-5.2 面向 GLM Coding Plan 全量用户开放，覆盖 Lite、Pro、Max 及团队版。该模型支持真正可用的 1M 上下文，在长程任务中保持领先，并被称为智谱最强的国产 Coding 模型。API 将于下周上线，模型将遵循 MIT 协议开源。文章强调前沿智能应开放、可用、可构建，服务于每一位开发者。",
